while (true)
{
    var frame = await sink.GetNextFrameAsync();
    // Process the frame (e.g., save it to a file, display it, etc.)
    // For example, to save the frame:
    frame.Save("C:\screenshots\frame.png", ImageFormat.Png, null, true);
}
```

#### 7. Stop the Capture and Dispose Resources
